{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sutherland-hodgman-polygon-clipping","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","demoType":null,"title":"Kukata mstatili wa Sutherland-Hodgman","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sutherland-Hodgman algoritam za odsecanje pronalazi mnogougao koji predstavlja presek proizvoljnog mnogougla (ulaznog mnogougla) i konveksnog mnogougla (mnogougla za odsecanje). Koristi se u računarskoj grafici (posebno 2D grafici) radi smanjenja složenosti scene uklanjanjem delova mnogougla koje nije potrebno prikazati. Posmatraj zatvoreni mnogougao definisan tačkama:</p>\n<pre>[(50, 150), (200, 50), (350, 150), (350, 300), (250, 300), (200, 250), (150, 350), (100, 250), (100, 200)]</pre>\n<p>Za pravougaonik definisan tačkama:</p>\n<pre>[(100, 100), (300, 100), (300, 300), (100, 300)]</pre>\n</section>","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8045","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napiši funkciju koja prihvata dva niza kao argumente. Prvi niz sadrži tačke ulaznog mnogougla, a drugi niz tačke mnogougla za odsecanje. Funkcija treba da vrati niz tačaka odsečenog mnogougla. Svaki broj treba zaokružiti na tri decimalna mesta.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Rosetta","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302336,"hooks":{"beforeAll":null,"beforeEach":"const subjectPolygon1 = [\n  [50, 150],\n  [200, 50],\n  [350, 150],\n  [350, 300],\n  [250, 300],\n  [200, 250],\n  [150, 350],\n  [100, 250],\n  [100, 200]\n];\nconst clipPolygon1 = [\n  [100, 100],\n  [300, 100],\n  [300, 300],\n  [100, 300]\n];\nconst expected1 = [\n  [100, 116.667],\n  [125, 100],\n  [275, 100],\n  [300, 116.667],\n  [300, 300],\n  [250, 300],\n  [200, 250],\n  [175, 300],\n  [125, 300],\n  [100, 250]\n];\n\nconst subjectPolygon2 = [\n  [150, 200],\n  [400, 450],\n  [30, 50]\n];\nconst clipPolygon2 = [\n  [10, 10],\n  [300, 200],\n  [400, 600],\n  [100, 300]\n];\nconst expected2 = [\n  [150, 200],\n  [350, 400],\n  [348.611, 394.444],\n  [30, 50]\n];\n\nconst subjectPolygon3 = [\n  [250, 200],\n  [100, 450],\n  [130, 250]\n];\nconst clipPolygon3 = [\n  [50, 60],\n  [100, 230],\n  [400, 600],\n  [100, 300]\n];\nconst expected3 = [\n  [129.167, 329.167],\n  [119.565, 319.565],\n  [121.854, 304.305]\n];","afterEach":null,"afterAll":null},"fields":{"slug":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sutherland-hodgman-polygon-clipping"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function clip(subjectPolygon, clipPolygon) {\n\n}","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>clip</code> Trebalo bi da bude funkcija.</p>","testString":"assert(typeof clip == 'function');"},{"text":"<p><code>clip([[50, 150], [200, 50], [350, 150], [350, 300], [250, 300], [200, 250], [150, 350], [100, 250], [100, 200]], [[100, 100], [300, 100], [300, 300], [100, 300]])</code> treba da vrati niz.</p>","testString":"assert(Array.isArray(clip(subjectPolygon1, clipPolygon1)));"},{"text":"<p><code>clip([[50, 150], [200, 50], [350, 150], [350, 300], [250, 300], [200, 250], [150, 350], [100, 250], [100, 200]], [[100, 100], [300, 100], [300, 300], [100, 300]])</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>[[100, 116.667], [125, 100], [275, 100], [300, 116.667], [300, 300], [250, 300], [200, 250], [175, 300], [125, 300], [100, 250]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(clip(subjectPolygon1, clipPolygon1), expected1);"},{"text":"<p><code>clip([[150, 200], [400, 450], [30, 50]], [[10, 10], [300, 200], [400, 600], [100, 300]])</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>[[150, 200], [350, 400], [348.611, 394.444], [30, 50]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(clip(subjectPolygon2, clipPolygon2), expected2);"},{"text":"<p><code>clip([[250, 200], [100, 450], [130, 250]], [[50, 60], [100, 230], [400, 600], [100, 300]])</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>[[129.167, 329.167], [119.565, 319.565], [121.854, 304.305]]</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.deepEqual(clip(subjectPolygon3, clipPolygon3), expected3);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/rosetta-code/#rosetta-code-challenges","dashedName":"sutherland-hodgman-polygon-clipping","certification":"rosetta-code","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"rosetta-code","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"rosetta-code-challenges","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/symmetric-difference","prevChallengePath":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sum-to-100","id":"5a23c84252665b21eecc8045","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function ZigZagMatrix(n) {\n  const mtx = [];\n  for (let i = 0; i < n; i++) {\n    mtx[i] = [];\n  }\n\n  let i = 1;\n  let j = 1;\n  for (let e = 0; e < n * n; e++) {\n    mtx[i - 1][j - 1] = e;\n    if ((i + j) % 2 === 0) {\n      // Even stripes\n      if (j < n) j++;\n      else i += 2;\n      if (i > 1) i--;\n    } else {\n      // Odd stripes\n      if (i < n) i++;\n      else j += 2;\n      if (j > 1) j--;\n    }\n  }\n  return mtx;\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/rosetta-code/rosetta-code-challenges/sutherland-hodgman-polygon-clipping"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}